trans-unit.source: Abstract class that, when implemented, defines an animation segment with its own target value and interpolation method for a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Abstrakt klass som implementeras definierar ett animering segment med sin egen mål värdet och interpolerade metod för en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Int32KeyFrame is an abstract class that defines <xref:System.Int32> value type key frames for several different techniques of key frame animation: <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.EasingInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineInt32KeyFrame>.
trans-unit.target: Int32KeyFrame är en abstrakt klass som definierar <xref:System.Int32>värde av typen key ramar för flera olika metoder för nyckelbilden animering: <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.EasingInt32KeyFrame> <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineInt32KeyFrame>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineInt32KeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearInt32KeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.EasingInt32KeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteInt32KeyFrame> </xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: To animate a <xref:System.Int32> value with key frames, you define a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames> animation, and populate its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames.KeyFrames%2A> property with one or more elements that define the key frames.
trans-unit.target: Att animera en <xref:System.Int32>värdet med viktiga ramar som du definierar en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames>animering, och fylla i dess <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames.KeyFrames%2A>egenskap med ett eller flera element som definierar nyckeln ramar.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames.KeyFrames%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames> </xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: For XAML syntaxes that take a Int32KeyFrame, you need to specify a non-abstract derived type of Int32KeyFrame as an object element.
trans-unit.target: För XAML-syntax som tar en Int32KeyFrame, måste du ange en icke-abstrakt härledd typ från Int32KeyFrame som ett objektelement.

trans-unit.source: For details, see the XAML syntax on the reference pages for <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.EasingInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineInt32KeyFrame>.
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i XAML-syntaxen på sidorna referens för <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.EasingInt32KeyFrame> <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineInt32KeyFrame>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineInt32KeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearInt32KeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.EasingInt32KeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteInt32KeyFrame>
